### Get all customers
GET https://{{ host }}/customers
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}

### Get a single customer
GET https://{{ host }}/customers/{{ test-customer-id }}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}

### Create a customer
POST https://{{ host }}/customers
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}

{
  "emailAddress": "{{ $random.email }}",
  "firstName": "Bob",
  "lastName": "Bobertson"
}

### Patch a customer
PATCH https://{{ host }}/customers/{{ test-customer-id }}
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}

{
  "firstName": "Bob"
}

### Delete a customer
DELETE https://{{ host }}/customers/nGN3dYwFfL3BzChcW9WQszXD
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ token }}